&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E7%BB%86%E8%8F%8C/#细胞壁">革兰氏阳性菌&lt;/a>：&lt;a scroll="葡萄球菌" class="anchor">葡萄球菌&lt;/a>、&lt;a scroll="链球菌" class="anchor">链球菌&lt;/a>、&lt;a scroll="肺炎链球菌" class="anchor">肺炎链球菌&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E5%8E%9F%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6/%E7%BB%86%E8%8F%8C/#细胞壁">革兰氏阴性菌&lt;/a>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>奈瑟菌属：&lt;a scroll="脑膜炎奈瑟菌" class="anchor">脑膜炎奈瑟菌&lt;/a>、&lt;a scroll="淋病奈瑟菌" class="anchor">淋病奈瑟菌&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>其他：&lt;a scroll="铜绿假单胞菌" class="anchor">铜绿假单胞菌&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
